01:32:38,934 --> 01:32:41,061
<i>leaving this a 20 to 14 football game.</i>

1042
01:32:41,144 --> 01:32:44,731
Why are they on the scoreboard?
They shouldn't even be in this game.

1043
01:32:44,815 --> 01:32:47,442
For the rest of your life,
you will remember today.

1044
01:32:47,568 --> 01:32:50,779
