you did not quit.

1046
01:32:53,448 --> 01:32:56,201
They're like little dogs
nipping at your heels.

1047
01:32:56,285 --> 01:32:58,579
Now get out there and stomp 'em.

1048
01:33:02,624 --> 01:33:06,086
That's what I'm talking about.
